text:
A bright-lit (with good natural light coming through) church hall with excellent vibe and very warm community groups. A great choice to hold a holy matrimony wedding ceremony. A multi-purpose space at first storey is good for food catering.
( Photos copyright @KAI_picture )
Great kindergarten that is operated by the church, especially if you want exposure of Mandarin to your child.
A building shared by an English language and a Chinese language Presbyterian churches. A good church for Hainanese.
Nice place of Worship and having Wedding. Easy access by Buses.
